formfiller

Class EventSources

  • java.lang.Object
    • formfiller.EventSources

  • public class EventSources
extends java.lang.Object
    The EventSources class stores a collection of EventSource objects. EventSources regulates the flow of user input by enabling or disabling each EventSource in the collection.
